[32m+[m[32mHeroku DB setup â†’ create app, add Postgres addon, reset, get DATABASE_URL.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mPythonAnywhere deploy â†’ clone repo, venv, install deps, create .env, configure WSGI.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mFinalization â†’ DB upgrade, create super admin, reload site.[m
